The window was left open to let some air in ‚Äî the heat made the room feel like an oven.

No one noticed the monkey wandering around the area during the day. It had been seen near the fence before, usually looking for food and running away whenever someone got close. This time, however, curiosity won.

The monkey climbed up to the open window, peered inside, and saw the guard asleep at the desk. On the table lay his equipment, neatly arranged, including the weapon he had placed down minutes before dozing off.

The monkey slipped through the window and reached for the object out of pure curiosity, grabbing it clumsily with both hands. The movement made noise, and the guard woke up halfway ‚Äî confused, still between sleep and reality ‚Äî reaching toward the table.

That‚Äôs when everything went wrong.

As the guard tried to take it back, the monkey‚Äôs grip tightened, and in the struggle the weapon fired. The shot echoed through the cabin, stunning the guard completely. He jumped up in shock, not understanding what had just happened.

This exact moment is what the camera captures.
